file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  title: Users
  contact: {}
  version: '1.0'
servers:
  - url: http://localhost:8081/api
    variables: {}
paths:
  /users/{id}/tasks:
    get:
      operationId: getMyTasks
      parameters:
        - in: query
          name: page
          schema:
            type: integer
          description: The number of records to skip before starting to collect
        - in: query
          name: limit
          schema:
            type: integer
          description: The number of records to return at once
        - in: path
          name: id
          schema:
            type: integer
          description: User id for fetching associated tasks
      tags:
        - users
      summary: Get my tasks
      responses:
        200:
          description: OK
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: array
                items:
                  $ref: "#/components/schemas/MyTaskResponse"
        403:
          description: Not authorized
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/responses/ForbiddenError'
  /users:
    post:
      operationId: createUsers
      requestBody:
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              type: array
              items:
                $ref: "#/components/schemas/CreateUserRequest"
      tags:
        - users
      summary: Create Users
      responses:
        200:
          description: OK
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: "#/components/schemas/CreateUserResponse"
        403:
          description: Not authorized
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/responses/ForbiddenError'


components:
  responses:
    ForbiddenError:
      description: error response for forbidden
      headers:
        WWW-Authenticate:
          schema:
            type: string
  schemas:
    CreateUserRequest:
      type: object
      properties:
        email:
          type: string
        name:
          type: string
      required:
        - email
        - name
    CreateUserResponse:
      type: object
      properties:
        id:
          type: integer
        email:
          type: string
        name:
          type: string
      required:
        - id
        - email
        - name
    MyTaskResponse:
      required:
        - id
        - rxNumber
        - patientFirstName
        - patientLastName
        - patientDob
        - drugName
        - doctorFirstName
        - doctorLastName
        - status
        - type
      type: object
      properties:
        id:
          type: integer
        rxNumber:
          type: string
        patientFirstName:
          type: string
        patientLastName:
          type: string
        patientDob:
          type: string
        drugName:
          type: string
        doctorName:
          type: string
        doctorLastName:
          type: string
        status:
          type: string
        type:
          type: string
        daysInProgress:
          type: integer
